## ‚úÖ What Works (MVP Complete)

‚úÖ **Smart Tokenization**: Handles strings with escape sequences (`\n`, `\t`, `\\`), numbers, identifiers, keywords, Brainfuck core operations[1]

‚úÖ **Error Recovery**: Graceful handling of unclosed strings, unknown characters, position tracking[1]

‚úÖ **Context-Aware Errors**: 4 skill levels (Beginner‚ÜíExpert), friendly messages, actionable suggestions[1][31][33]

‚úÖ **Semantic Intent Detection**: Identifies programming patterns (assignment, conditional, iteration), generates AI-ready context[1][36][39]

‚úÖ **Confidence Tracking**: Records user actions, calculates success rates, suggests skill progression[1]

‚úÖ **Multi-Model AI Ready**: Semantic context formatted for Claude, GPT-4, Ollama APIs[1][16][19]

‚úÖ **Accessibility Compliant**: Follows WCAG 2.2 AAA + neurodivergent design principles[17][20][37]

